{"@context":"http://iiif.io/api/presentation/3/context.json","id":"https://digbmc.github.io/pta-manifests/phan/phan-01619/manifest.json","type":"Manifest","label":{"none":["PHAN-01619"]},"metadata":[{"label":{"none":["Timestamp"]},"value":{"none":["0:16:19"]}},{"label":{"none":["Film"]},"value":{"none":["Phantom Thread"]}},{"label":{"none":["Creator"]},"value":{"none":["Paul Thomas Anderson"]}},{"label":{"none":["Distance"]},"value":{"none":["full shot"]}},{"label":{"none":["Angle"]},"value":{"none":["low"]}},{"label":{"none":["Location"]},"value":{"none":["exterior"]}},{"label":{"none":["Movement"]},"value":{"none":["mobile, pan"]}},{"label":{"none":["Lighting"]},"value":{"none":["low key"]}},{"label":{"none":["Composition"]},"value":{"none":["two shot"]}}],"summary":{"none":["A man helps a woman into a car."]},"thumbnail":[{"id":"https://digitalscholarship.brynmawr.edu/pta/phan/phan-01619/tiles/full/300,169/0/default.jpg","type":"Image","format":"image/jpeg","height":169,"width":300}],"homepage":[{"id":"PHAN-01619","type":"Text","format":"text/html","label":{"none":["Object homepage"]}}],"items":[{"id":"https://digitalscholarship.brynmawr.edu/pta/phan/phan-01619/canvas/1","type":"Canvas","height":1080,"width":1920,"label":{"none":["PHAN-01619"]},"thumbnail":[{"id":"https://digitalscholarship.brynmawr.edu/pta/phan/phan-01619/tiles/full/300,169/0/default.jpg","type":"Image","format":"image/jpeg","height":169,"width":300}],"items":[{"id":"https://digitalscholarship.brynmawr.edu/pta/phan/phan-01619/canvas/1/annopage-1","type":"AnnotationPage","items":[{"id":"https://digitalscholarship.brynmawr.edu/pta/phan/phan-01619/canvas/1/annopage-1/anno-1","type":"Annotation","motivation":"painting","target":"https://digitalscholarship.brynmawr.edu/pta/phan/phan-01619/canvas/1","body":{"id":"https://digitalscholarship.brynmawr.edu/pta/phan/phan-01619/tiles/full/1920,1080/0/default.jpg","type":"Image","format":"image/jpeg","height":1080,"width":1920,"service":[{"id":"https://digitalscholarship.brynmawr.edu/pta/phan/phan-01619/tiles","type":"ImageService3","profile":"http://iiif.io/api/image/3/level0.json"}]}}]}],"annotations":[{"id":"https://digitalscholarship.brynmawr.edu/pta/phan/phan-01619/canvas/1/page/p1","type":"AnnotationPage","items":[{"id":"https://digitalscholarship.brynmawr.edu/pta/phan/phan-01619/canvas/1/ccc27c4f-d539-44ac-bd61-20286ae47fe1","type":"Annotation","motivation":"commenting","body":[{"created":"2026-07-01T14:34:50.996Z","creator":"Clara Smith","purpose":"commenting","type":"TextualBody","format":"text/html","value":"<p>Reynolds and Alma’s date takes place at night, which contrasts with their first meeting at the Victoria Hotel restaurant and the lighthearted tone of that encounter. Instead, the darkness present conceals the many secrets that lurk behind the façade of what begins as an idyllic romance. Unsurprisingly, Reynolds is in the driver’s seat. In opening the door to his car, he also lets Alma into his life.&nbsp;</p>"}],"target":{"type":"SpecificResource","source":"https://digitalscholarship.brynmawr.edu/pta/phan/phan-01619/canvas/1","selector":{"type":"FragmentSelector","conformsTo":"http://www.w3.org/TR/media-frags/","value":"xywh=pixel:1343.711790393013,561.528384279476,307.3144104803496,335.14192139737986"}}},{"id":"https://digitalscholarship.brynmawr.edu/pta/phan/phan-01619/canvas/1/79adfb4f-9191-4088-8877-e33fec0ce254","type":"Annotation","motivation":"commenting","body":[{"created":"2026-07-01T14:35:03.029Z","creator":"Clara Smith","purpose":"commenting","type":"TextualBody","format":"text/html","value":"<p>Reynolds’ question of whether he is late offers Alma the opportunity to say “no” again to a man whose power enables him to often hear “yes.” Even though the negative response is a pleasing one (he does not want to be late), it recalls their first encounter and Alma’s first word to him.&nbsp;&nbsp;</p>"}],"target":{"type":"SpecificResource","source":"https://digitalscholarship.brynmawr.edu/pta/phan/phan-01619/canvas/1","selector":{"type":"FragmentSelector","conformsTo":"http://www.w3.org/TR/media-frags/","value":"xywh=pixel:1321.353711790393,229.26855895196502,300.4148471615722,153.231441048035"}}}]}]}]}